Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.54,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:12.08,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.71,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.35,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.77,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:18.04,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.66,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.54,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:12.08,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.71,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.35,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.77,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:18.04,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.66,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Turquoise for H.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Bronze for A-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:46.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Brownish green for three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.86,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, this should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Please go with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.01,clover,,0,0,0,,You seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.37,clover,,0,0,0,,What else are you working on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:05.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, they're adding another room at the Kosouan, so I'll be making pottery for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:08.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh... the Kosouan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the one in Kamakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:13.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a wonderful venue that was converted from an old private home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.59,clover,,0,0,0,,You work for some amazing places.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.35,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Rika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.43,clover,,0,0,0,,She really got me a lot of connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san really must like your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:30.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Things seem like they're going well. Now is when you need to work hard, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:32.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san is working in Spain right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing that she gets to work at the Valencia Museum of Art?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.79,clover,,0,0,0,,You're right... That is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:54.03,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Rika-san left for Spain last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but Mayama didn't go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:01.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened between the two of them before she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.77,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I can tell something has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:16.73,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, when she calls, a new voice, calmer and deeper than before, will flow through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:23.28,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She has opened her heart to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.08,clover,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, Yamada-san, shall we go somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.12,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you're staying home, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.64,sign,,0,0,0,,Health Land
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.93,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Miwako-san... t-this place is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.25,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, we're gonna enjoy this to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.54,clover,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.72,clover,,0,0,0,,But... I... Miwako-san... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.80,clover,,0,0,0,,The rose and fruit bath really is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.17,clover,,0,0,0,,A p-pineapple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:23.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay... After we warm up, we're getting a body scrub!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
