Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.93,clover,,0,0,0,,It feels like I have new skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Now then, we're off to our next stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san! Isn't this one piece nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I should call this a muumuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:11.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is barefoot, has no makeup on, and is wearing the same muumuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Viva Health Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.75,clover,,0,0,0,,It's strange. Wearing these clothes makes me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:29.32,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's basically impossible to think of sad things when you're wearing a flowery muumuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, we're gonna experience everything this place has to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.84,note,,0,0,0,,[ Edamame is boiled and lightly salted green soybeans ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.84,clover,,0,0,0,,How about we start off with some draft beer and edamame?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.76,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:59.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're trying to cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada-san, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.62,clover,,0,0,0,,I thought something smelled nice. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:14.57,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ureshii nukumori ni tsutsumareru tame\NLonging for the happiness in my warm embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Fragrant olives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:19.93,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}ikutsu mo no machigai kasaneteru\NYou repeat the same mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:23.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Every year, when the city is filled with the scent of this flower, preparations for the school festival begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:22.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}je t'aime...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:28.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}baka da yo na\NYou're such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Bathed in the orange glow of the school's lights, and surrounded by the scent of the fragrant olives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:34.35,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}betsu ni kamawanai to kimi wa iu kedo\NYou say that you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:34.95,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...I'd keep wandering the places I thought I might see the person I like so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.41,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tekitou na kotoba ga mitsukaranai\NAnd I can't find the words to play it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted to catch just a glimpse of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.07,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}je t'aime...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.07,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:48.06,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sonna toko da\NThat's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My long...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.40,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Long...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:58.09,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi ga iru no wa ikenai koto da\NBut you shouldn't be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.77,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.37,clover,,0,0,0,,It smells so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.44,clover,,0,0,0,,It's my favorite flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:08.85,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nayami tsukareta kyou mo mata\NI'm tired from all the worrying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Do you like the fragrant olives, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's drink, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Now drink and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:27.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Once we've eaten, we're going to the pool, the massage room, and the germanium bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.05,clover,,0,0,0,,We're doing the full course tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:39.46,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi ga iru no wa suteki na koto da\NIt's nice that you're here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:49.34,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}yasashiku naru nani mo kamo\NIt makes everything more kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.71,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(387,143)\fad(279,230)}Hey, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.71,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(387,170)\fad(279,230)}Yamada-san! Welcome~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.92,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, that did the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:59.15,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi ga iru no wa ikenai koto da\NBut you shouldn't be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nomiya, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:10.17,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nayami tsukareta kyou mo mata\NI'm tired from all the worrying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san is right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.94,clover,,0,0,0,,She's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:12.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I basically wore her out with a full course at the Health Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Sis... you wore her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, something did between Mayama and Rika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Was she crying again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.27,clover,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.98,clover,,0,0,0,,But she's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.84,clover,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping with her beautiful legs all exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.11,clover,,0,0,0,,...in her underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.59,clover,,0,0,0,,I wanna see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.35,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(360,263)\fad(231,186)}Oh my, Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.78,clover,,0,0,0,,You're too honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.40,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Please take care of her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:51.19,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd welcome a girl this pretty any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.79,clover,,0,0,0,,But you know, Mayama's pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:09:02.38,clover,,0,0,0,,He was around a girl with her figure day in and day out and didn't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.27,clover,,0,0,0,,She must've really been precious to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.91,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She must've really been precious to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:21.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't that damn adolescent give me a call?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.27,clover,,0,0,0,,I hadn't heard from her so I figured she was doing well, and now this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Was that an S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna go to her, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:33.97,clover,,0,0,0,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.71,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.16,clover,,0,0,0,,She can cry by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:42.15,clover,,0,0,0,,N-Nomiya...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:00.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to come back in a little bit... just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.85,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please don't cry all by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Don't cry in front of some other guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.36,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.22,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:22.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The sand from those dunes, his expression, and his words...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.79,thoughts,,0,0,0,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.67,clover,,0,0,0,,M-M-M-M-M-Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:45.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating someone else's food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:51.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm broke this month because I put all my money into getting a license!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:57.39,clover,,0,0,0,,My plan to make it through to next month with just 100 yen bread crusts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:01.49,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun, you can have my steamed bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.27,clover,,0,0,0,,It's okay, isn't that your lunch, Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.06,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Please eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.64,clover,,0,0,0,,No{\fscx200}-{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.89,clover,,0,0,0,,That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:18.96,clover,,0,0,0,,That is so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takemoto, am I that dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.10,clover,,0,0,0,,It's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Am I so dirty that she has to rush to wash her hands with soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.27,clover,,0,0,0,,You're filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Like the part where you put on little acts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.51,clover,,0,0,0,,And the part where you eat other people's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.76,clover,,0,0,0,,In fact, you're pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.03,clover,,0,0,0,,You've been a smartass lately, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.56,clover,,0,0,0,,You're yelling back at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't make a fuss here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.82,clover,,0,0,0,,If you get in the way of Hagu's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.10,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:48.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Or you know what, become one with the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.00,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,118)\c&H8C9695&\3c&HEAF3F9&\b1\fnCalibri\fs36}2nd {\b0}Floor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Like, heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh no, my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.67,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:12:00.50,clover,,0,0,0,,William, Bill, Billie! I'm gonna save you all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:05.48,clover,,0,0,0,,If have that much money, why are you eating my food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.94,clover,,0,0,0,,I got them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.71,clover,,0,0,0,,They all came back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.82,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you do for your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.46,clover,,0,0,0,,You work so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.25,clover,,0,0,0,,But you don't seem to be spending any...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.95,clover,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you gonna do with that much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.89,clover,,0,0,0,,Yo, I've been waiting for you, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show this to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.31,clover,,0,0,0,,It's finally complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:59.47,clover,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect system to swindle 50 yen a month from every kid in the world forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.91,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Look, Shiroyama is so touched that he's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.70,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I think Shiroyama is crying for a different reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. We'll stop kidding around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:17.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, can you do another job before next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.60,clover,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.78,clover,,0,0,0,,On what scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Hundred of millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Shiroyama, reduce the timetable from forever to one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:32.85,clover,,0,0,0,,And switch "every kid" to "every single person under thirty" and see what numbers come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll take that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Have you been sleeping properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.17,clover,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.56,clover,,0,0,0,,For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.79,clover,,0,0,0,,You should sleep more, or you'll dull your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:51.91,clover,,0,0,0,,And don't make any flashy moves. They'll catch onto us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.71,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from you, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.93,clover,,0,0,0,,How much longer do we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:06.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Just one last push to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:14.02,clover,,0,0,0,,You take things too far, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:18.56,clover,,0,0,0,,I understand that you wanted to get your license right away, but you didn't need to invest all of your daily living money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.13,clover,,0,0,0,,This tastes great, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.81,clover,,0,0,0,,I can feel the grains of rice spreading through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Fill yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.10,clover,,0,0,0,,But Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.79,clover,,0,0,0,,What was the big hurry to get your license?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.79,clover,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:46.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If you want to work for us, you should get your driver's license while you're still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, during your trip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.31,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:56.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:01.48,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be paying for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.69,clover,,0,0,0,,So let's go to the bath house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:06.64,clover,,0,0,0,,And I'll even buy you an ice cream at the convenience store on the way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:11.98,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll seriously never forget this gratitude, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Um... Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:23.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Why do you still live in that apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:28.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Since you have a job, shouldn't you be able to rent a better room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Well... it's because there's something I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I'm saving up for when that time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.38,clover,,0,0,0,,For when that time comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.46,clover,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:42.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't even know if that time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.04,clover,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I read in some book...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.91,clover,,0,0,0,,...that every human has at least three opportunities in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.44,clover,,0,0,0,,And I thought this as I grew up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:16:03.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling it's a matter of having the money to take advantage of that opportunity when it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:08.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-san, could it be that you have a significant savings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.64,clover,,0,0,0,,So I'm the only one that is actually poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:16.35,clover,,0,0,0,,You're fine since you're still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.23,clover,,0,0,0,,So you're preparing yourself for that opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.31,clover,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to the woman I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:31.64,clover,,0,0,0,,...I want to have enough to be able to tell her, "Go ahead and take some time off."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.90,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.39,clover,,0,0,0,,That was hammy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.37,clover,,0,0,0,,I admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll say it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.75,clover,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.13,clover,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.43,clover,,0,0,0,,I need to wash off this hammy stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Better yet, please forget it, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Please forget I said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:02.04,clover,,0,0,0,,No, you're brilliant, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.07,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to the woman I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:22.14,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...I want to have enough to be able to tell her, "Go ahead and take some time off."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:27.00,clover,,0,0,0,,I really agreed with Mayama-san's words back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.66,clover,,0,0,0,,But... all I could do was agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.59,clover,,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.90,clover,,0,0,0,,...don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.00,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.97,clover,,0,0,0,,We had you come all the way out here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:50.23,clover,,0,0,0,,I really wonder where Miwako-san went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.53,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,186)\pos(466,231)}Ah, it's Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Takaido-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:02.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Leader, Leader, you're such a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.12,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,182)\an1\pos(445,269)}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.12,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,182)\an1\pos(445,294)}That's a new song,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.12,dog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,182)\an1\pos(493,319)}Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:07.42,clover,,0,0,0,,The backs of your legs are so fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:12.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you wonder where Miwako-san went, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Health Land was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.49,clover,,0,0,0,,We drank beer together under the fragrant olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.56,clover,,0,0,0,,The fragrant olives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:37.50,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, when you feel helpless, please call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.02,thoughts,,0,0,0,,When you feel helpless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.79,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(588,266)\fad(230,186)}Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome back, Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.41,clover,,0,0,0,,N-Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.63,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,423)\fad(193,142)}Nomiya-san,\NNomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:05.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leader. How've ya been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. You're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.92,clover,,0,0,0,,And Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:30.01,clover,,0,0,0,,A r-roundhouse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:38.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I ran out because it felt like he saw right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I honestly wanted to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.01,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted to listen to a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to ask him so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:53.90,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but I hated myself for thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:20:03.99,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, if I thought that, all of my feelings for Mayama would turn into lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:16.92,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I don't care how pathetic or embarrassing I look in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:22.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,My feelings for him... only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:27.17,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...was my bittersweet treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.24,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:52.54,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep crying over Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.17,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:04.02,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that he came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:12.57,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...it hurts so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:30.10,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:30.10,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:40.26,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:40.26,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.68,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.68,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:53.22,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:53.22,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:06.29,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:06.29,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:09.03,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:09.03,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.89,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.89,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.53,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.53,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:24.93,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:24.93,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:28.63,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:28.63,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:34.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: We were never to go to the beach.
